{"about_the_game":"Magic the Wandering is a Lemmings inspired roguelite puzzle platformer about helping lost wizards find a way through different dimensions.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119890/extras/mtw_prot.gif?t=1727107198\" /><br><br>Learn spells and unlock wizard types as you progress through and try to beat the highest score and level reached. Uncover secret achievements to get some of the more powerful unlocks to help you on your next run or power up your current progress.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119890/extras/mtw_fight.gif?t=1727107198\" /><br><br>The true Lemmings successor.<br>Every stage has multiple ways of getting to the end and overcome all the obstacles.<br>Normal mode with more wizards to start with. Challenge yourself with the Highlander mode where you only have one wizard the whole run.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119890/extras/wizard_attack_red.gif?t=1727107198\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119890/extras/wizard_prot_cast.gif?t=1727107198\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119890/extras/wizard_camo_walk.gif?t=1727107198\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119890/extras/wizard_blue_walk.gif?t=1727107198\" /><br><br>Use different wizard types with their own special abilities.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> learn spells for all wizards to use<br></li><li> modifiers for spells to alter their effects<br></li><li> find and unlock different wizard types useable for subsequent runs<br></li><li> progressive difficulty increase per each level<br></li><li> environment specific hazards and enemies<br></li><li> try to rank up in a global le